c: 8
v: 36
t: "“Ndithu osakhulupirira akupereka chuma chawo (pa nkhondo yolimbana ndi Asilamu) ndi cholinga choti awatsekeleze anthu kuyenda pa njira ya Allah. Choncho adzapitiriza kupereka chumacho kenako chidzakhala chowadandaulitsa, ndipo adzagonjetsedwa. Ndipo omwe sanakhulupirire adzasonkhanitsidwa ku Jahannam"